OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776856004
OL,3,CNike accused of 'shaming' participants
OL,4,Cwho walk in local Parkrun event
OL,6,FNike has faced criticism for "shaming"
OL,7,Fparticipants in local Parkrun events
OL,8,Fafter releasing a set of adverts aimed
OL,9,Fat discouraging walking.
OL,11,FSigns baring the Nike tick alongside
OL,12,Fstatements such as "You didn't come
OL,13,Fall this way for a walk in the park"
OL,14,For "Running in London is peak"
OL,15,Fappeared in several parks across
OL,16,FLondon this month, including in
OL,17,FCrystal Palace Park, Brockwell Park
OL,18,Fand Peckham Rye.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
