FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776856004
OL,3,CNike accused of 'shaming' participants
OL,4,Cwho walk in local Parkrun event
OL,6,FSome of the displays were hanging from
OL,7,Fcherry pickers, while other smaller
OL,8,Fsigns directed people around paths
OL,9,Fwith the signage: "Runners only".
OL,11,FKirsty Woodbridge, head of
OL,12,Fcommunications at parkrun UK,
OL,13,Fdenounced the campaign in a statement
OL,14,Fon LinkedIn, telling Nike that its
OL,15,F"elitist messaging is not welcome at
OL,16,Fparkrun".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776856004
OL,3,CNike accused of 'shaming' participants
OL,4,Cwho walk in local Parkrun event
OL,6,FMs Woodbridge said the messaging puts
OL,7,F"incredible and totally unnecessary
OL,8,Fpressure on the local people", adding
OL,9,Fthat people come to walk in parks for
OL,10,Fmany reasons, from health conditions
OL,11,Fto seeking social connection.
OL,13,F"To anyone thinking about coming to
OL,14,Fparkrun, walking, running,
OL,15,Fvolunteering, coming to watch,
OL,16,Fwhatever the hell you like, ignore
OL,17,Fthis rubbish," she wrote.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
