OL,3,CNike accused of 'shaming' participants
OL,4,Cwho walk in local Parkrun event
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FNike did not immediately respond to
OL,12,FITV News' request for comment.
OL,14,FHowever, in a statement to the Times,
OL,15,Fthe sportswear company apologised and
OL,16,Fadmitted it had "missed the mark".
OL,18,F"We'll use this moment to do better
OL,19,Fand continue showing up for all
OL,20,Frunners," it said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
