OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1776856004
OL,3,CNike accused of 'shaming' participants
OL,4,Cwho walk in local Parkrun event
OL,6,FNike was forced to take down a similar
OL,7,Fcampaign poster that read "Runners
OL,8,Fwelcome, walkers tolerated" ahead of
OL,9,Fthe Boston marathon last week after
OL,10,Fonline backlash.
OL,12,FWoodbridge's LinkedIn statement
OL,13,Fprompted runners and parkrun
OL,14,Fvolunteers to call out Nike's
OL,15,Fmessaging for being "inappropriate",
OL,16,F"rude" and the "opposite of
OL,17,Finclusivity".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
