OL,3,CNike accused of 'shaming' participants
OL,4,Cwho walk in local Parkrun event
OL,6,FParkrun CEO Lil Duggan told ITV News:
OL,7,F"Everyone is welcome, regardless of
OL,8,Fpace, background, or ability. All
OL,9,Fparticipants are celebrated, whether
OL,10,Fthey choose to walk, run, volunteer or
OL,11,Fsimply come along to support those
OL,12,Ftaking part and soak up the feel good
OL,13,Fatmosphere."
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
